                    <span class="mask_title_head">一.如何获得@(WorkContext.SellerInfo.ScoreName)？</span> <br>
					1.新用户注册（绑定手机号）获得<span style="color: #f00;">@(WorkContext.SellerInfo.RegisterGiftScore)</span>@(WorkContext.SellerInfo.ScoreName) <br>
