					2.用户A分享二维码，未关注的用户B扫此二维码，关注公众号，用户A获得<span style="color: #f00;">@(WorkContext.SellerInfo.ShareGiftScore)</span>@(WorkContext.SellerInfo.ScoreName) <br>
